text: Alcalá de Guadaíra is a municipality of 75,917 people (2022). It is in the province of Seville in the autonomous community of Andalusia in south Spain. The city is 15 km southeast of Seville, on the river Guadaíra. Category:Province of Seville Category:Municipalities in Andalusia
title: Alcalá de Guadaíra
